title: The Story That Made Amy Cry + Is Raymundo’s Vegas Bachelor Party Back On? + The Dumb Things We Believed As Kids
itunes:title: The Story That Made Amy Cry + Is Raymundo’s Vegas Bachelor Party Back On? + The Dumb Things We Believed As Kids
description:
Amy shares a story about a FedEx driver helping out a kid that made her cry yesterday. Raymundo says his Las Vegas bachelor party is still happening and it's going down at the end of June. The guys debate if they'll still go. Plus, we all share dumb things we believed as kids. Bobby thought babies came out of belly buttons!
